repos.name: chiasmodon
repos.description: Chiasmodon is an OSINT  tool designed to assist in the process of gathering information about a target domain. Its primary functionality revolves around searching for domain-related data, including domain emails, domain credentials, CIDRs , ASNs , and subdomains, the tool also allows users to search Google Play application ID.
